"how to configure the workflow section."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For an overview about proposals, see <xref linkend=\"ex-fb-proposal\"/> . "
"This provides you with enough background to modify the firstboot "
"installation workflow. The basic syntax of the firstboot configuration file "
"(plus how the key elements are configured) is explained with this example."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring the Proposal Screens"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    &hellip;\n"
"    &lt;proposals config:type=\"list\"&gt;<co xml:id=\"co-fb-plist\"/>\n"
