#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:589
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make changes to the number or order of proposal screens during the "
"firstboot installation, proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the firstboot configuration file at <filename>/etc/YaST2/firstboot.xml</"
"filename> ."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete or add proposal screens or change the order of the existing ones:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete an entire proposal, remove the <literal>proposal</literal> element "
"including all its sub-elements from the <literal>proposals</literal> section "
"and remove the respective <literal>module</literal> element (with sub-"
"elements) from the workflow."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a new proposal, create a new <literal>proposal</literal> element and "
"fill in all the required sub-elements. Make sure that the proposal exists as "
"a &yast; module in <filename>/usr/share/YaST2/clients</filename> ."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the order of proposals, move the respective <literal>module</"
"literal> elements containing the proposal screens around in the workflow. "
"Note that there may be dependencies to other installation steps that require "
"a certain order of proposals and workflow components."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can always change the workflow of the configuration steps when the "
"default does not meet your needs. Enable or disable certain modules in the "
"workflow (or add your own custom ones)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To toggle the status of a module in the firstboot workflow, proceed as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the value for the <literal>enabled</literal> element from "
"<literal>true</literal> to <filename>false</filename> to disable the module "
"or from <literal>false</literal> to <literal>true</literal> to enable it "
"again."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#: deployment_firstboot.xml:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"&lt;module&gt;\n"
"    &lt;label&gt;Time and Date&lt;/label&gt;\n"
"    &lt;enabled config:type=\"boolean\"&gt;true&lt;/enabled&gt;\n"
